title: CHIR Revitalized Tourism Lines from Changchun to Hunchun (People's Government of Jilin Province)
text: ( Source : People's Government of Jilin Province ) Changchun-Hunchun Intercity Railway ( CHIR ) that was open to traffic on September 20 has revitalized along nine-station tourism lines in the 'October 1' Golden Week and made border city Hunchun
